{"updated_at": "2012-05-08T18:50:50Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2012-05-08T18:50:50Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5583051", "id": 5583051, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5362", "issue_id": 5362, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/rroblak", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "16f606d6f3cd4f7b742ec0d6db1674bf", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/16f606d6f3cd4f7b742ec0d6db1674bf?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F4df49b56bc16bcda30bb2dac13bce603.png", "id": 103835, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/events{/privacy}", "login": "rroblak", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rroblak/followers"}, "body": "This patch handles that case:\r\n\r\n```\r\n1.9.3p125 :002 > Challenge.where(:type => [SpecialChallenge, DifficultChallenge])\r\n  Challenge Load (0.6ms)  SELECT \"challenges\".* FROM \"challenges\" WHERE \"challenges\".\"type\" IN ('SpecialChallenge', 'DifficultChallenge')\r\n => []\r\n```\r\n\r\nA test for that case would be outside the scope of this patch, since `ActiveRecord::ConnectionAdapters::Quoting#quote` is only concerned with quoting individual parameters. I believe [Arel](https://github.com/rails/arel) handles building arrays.", "_id": {"$oid": "5238195cbd3543c15100e17b"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5362#issuecomment-5583051"}
